2004-02-09 22:36  kelnos

	* configure.ac, menu.xml, src/Makefile.am, src/dummy.h,
	  src/dummy.png, src/menu-dentry.c, src/menu-dentry.h,
	  src/menu-file.c, src/menu-file.h, src/menu-icon.c,
	  src/menu-icon.h, src/menu.c, src/menu.h, src/menuspec.c,
	  src/menuspec.h, src/xfce-registered-categories.xml: menu icon
	  support for the desktop menu! quick summary: *major code reorg
	  *menu icon support *new <include> tag for menu.xml *autogenerated
	  menus via the freedesktop.org menu spec NOTE: SVG icon support
	  disabled pending resolution of major memory leaks	  in
	  librsvg and/or the SVG gdk-pixbuf loader

